    "text": [
        "Hi Abhinav,",
        "How're you? Hope this letter finds you well! I'm writing to let you, I've finally decided to resign from my job and started looking for a new one.",
        "The thing is, without boring you with details, I've been put under a huge amount of pressure at work, lately, to complete the tasks in an unreasonable timeframe. The resulting stress was clouding my brain and now I've decided to leave this company and work for something I'm passionate about.",
        "Perhaps, I'm thinking to join a wealth management company. As you already know, I always do investments to generate a secondary source of income and I believe, I'm quite experienced in it now. My knowledge about finance can help individuals to build a fortune out of their hard-earned money.",
        "Since you're already working with a similar agency, I was thinking if you can write a letter of reference for me. Your reference towards my attitude and aptitude will have a salutary effect on my application. Moreover, It would be great if you can advise me on prioritising the companies for which I should be applying first.",
        "Waiting for your response eagerly.",
        "Regards,",
        "Rubina"
    ],
